{"tid":1439577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【經濟戰第一波】罷買？你地對唔對得住香港人？","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:42:28.000Z","uid":70786,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7310a84c0c95cb9980c539e67f3076515beebc38","tid":1439577,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:03:53.000Z","msg":"林鄭同零售餐飲業齊聲指責示威活動令本地經濟失速<br />\n要拆招除咗星期五日罷買儲錢，同時亦要<span style=\"color: red;\">每週一日爆買</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆買唔係乜狗屎垃圾商店都買喎<br />\n而係揀d有良心，有參與兩次罷工嘅香港舖頭買！<br />\n每週去表揚唔同商店，幫佢地搵翻罷工而蝕咗嘅生意額！<br />\n要佢地生意好到可以投放更多資源參與抗爭<br />\n甚至係擴張規模開多D分店，創造更多就業機會！<br />\n<br />\n個活動要搞到一田大減價咁墟憾，傳媒都去採訪，愈多傳媒愈好<br />\n我地多人但一定會好有秩序，唔會好似D師奶餓狗搶屎咁<br />\n弱智藍絲見到多人排自己又會排埋一份驚死執輸<br />\n咁做可以抗衡政府想營造百業蕭條嘅景象<br />\n令大大小小零售餐飲店質疑政府「點解佢多我咁多生意？公平咩？」<br />\n最後仲可能表態歸邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場戰爭係長期戰<br />\n完全罷買係好難持續，有見及此<br />\n暫定每星期一／四全城爆買<br />\n買定日用品為星期五日罷買做好準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大家都可以係屋企開開心心hea住過<br />\n<br />\n以下為投票環節<br />\n星期一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次活動目標暫定阿布泰國生活百貨<br />\n點解揀佢？因為香港仆街政府有負於佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而佢賣生活百貨，可以幫大家漫長抗爭做準備<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190715/20729588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F20729588&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68sxX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=71749b92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F20729588&h=d84aa5be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190715/20729588</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">阿布泰國生活百貨創辦人林景楠昨參與沙田遊行，他前日在facebook發帖透露自己是2015年參與「光復沙田」後被政府因網上言論而解僱的海關關員，呼籲市民參與沙田遊行。林昨表示，再在沙田遊行感觸特別大，強調言論自由是香港核心價值，無論何人都不能阻止他發聲，「我作為商人，商人就有我哋嘅社會責任，更加要企出嚟發聲」。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於去邊間分店<br />\n鑽石山，荃灣同銅鑼灣會唔會最方便各區巴絲打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揀三間係想集中人流<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.abouthai.com/locations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abouthai.com%2Flocations&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68sxX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=7ea2b147\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.abouthai.com/locations</a><br />\n元朗分店就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間：暫定放工時間下午6點，大家買完野可以返屋企睇下Netflix chill下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家提供任何意見<br />\n活動成型後會再出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一波揀邊間商舖都可以提議下<br />\n我就提名袁彌明生活百貨<br />\n俾D為香港仆心仆命嘅絲打買護膚品，扮靚靚心情都靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d52cef988498e2f7f5b716b9a002030eff11f1","tid":1439577,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"一齊救手足！<br />\n<br />\n見到班防暴做埋畜蟲既野，就諗起自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb330b3f39030c96e13439fb9fb7f1d62f28cdf0","tid":1439577,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳] 支持黃商抵制藍商救港app「自由篩」已成形，短期內推出上架<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/acEQNhU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/acEQNhU</a>"},{"pid":"bb707897860cfef28d29510b72f9358133095011","tid":1439577,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"可能會混淆咗大家<br />\n<br />\n再開過投票環節<br />\n星期一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0872bf4ddd11e741b9fc6cba95565dc6b59ff4","tid":1439577,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無大台 只有自己代表到自己<br />\n不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"930fc952acea2b143812f28d96b7b0f247b4a0cc","tid":1439577,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c357821b84899f95b202884a2b52d289bde85eae","tid":1439577,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6fb2e57ca90746646fec87228aae80678ecd0fe","tid":1439577,"uid":170014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"其實一早有文宣講罷買<br />\n但我個人覺得唔夠全面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLieGJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLieGJM.jpg&h=968fa311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUGctoN.jpg\" data-thumbna